00:31:43,260 --> 00:31:44,430
Here, have some tea.

572
00:31:50,350 --> 00:31:52,210
I'm afraid I won't be able to enjoy

573
00:31:52,390 --> 00:31:54,120
next year's fresh Longjing tea

574
00:31:55,030 --> 00:31:56,560
before Tomb-Sweeping Day.

575
00:32:00,230 --> 00:32:02,230
It must be quite lively outside now.

576
00:32:05,430 --> 00:32:07,750
Suzhou people only do this on Chinese New Year's Eve.

577
00:32:07,750 --> 00:32:12,980
[We don't know whether we're crazy or stupid] [All we can do is move forward]

578
00:32:11,550 --> 00:32:13,310
I really like Suzhou.

579
00:32:13,870 --> 00:32:15,400
Unfortunately, my wish...

580
00:32:16,830 --> 00:32:19,070
The people of Amaterasu

581
00:32:19,990 --> 00:32:22,160
can't live in Suzhou anymore.

582
00:32:25,030 --> 00:32:26,270
I'm sorry about that.

583
00:32:27,910 --> 00:32:28,990
You Japanese should live

584
00:32:28,990 --> 00:32:30,030
on your own land.

585
00:32:34,110 --> 00:32:35,200
Do you know?

586
00:32:35,870 --> 00:32:38,470
I always thought that Zhou Zhifei was my enemy,

587
00:32:39,270 --> 00:32:40,790
but actually, you're

588
00:32:41,550 --> 00:32:42,830
my real opponent.

589
00:32:45,740 --> 00:32:47,870
Although you and I are on different sides,

590
00:32:47,870 --> 00:32:49,550
I respect you very much.

591
00:32:50,870 --> 00:32:51,950
Because you and I

592
00:32:52,440 --> 00:32:53,750
are people of faith.

593
00:32:58,060 --> 00:33:01,790
Japan lost this war.

594
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:09,230
However,

595
00:33:10,750 --> 00:33:12,070
as a soldier,

596
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:21,130
I must be responsible for this.

597
00:33:27,870 --> 00:33:28,510
Mr. Gu,

598
00:33:30,490 --> 00:33:33,240
please be my kaishakunin.

599
00:33:39,570 --> 00:33:41,530
You want me to behead you

600
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:44,300
after you disembowel yourself?

601
00:35:45,950 --> 00:35:47,470
The Commander-in-Chief of the Kuomintang

602
00:35:47,470 --> 00:35:49,600
Military Commission's Special Operations for Suzhou

603
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:50,570
is here!

604
00:35:55,670 --> 00:35:56,590
Major!

605
00:35:58,250 --> 00:35:59,260
What happened?

606
00:36:00,270 --> 00:36:01,650
Zhou Zhifei!

607
00:36:02,060 --> 00:36:03,240
I'm Zhou Youren.

608
00:36:03,580 --> 00:36:04,550
Zhou Zhifei

609
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:06,830
is the alias I used

610
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:09,100
while I was an undercover at No. 90.

611
00:36:09,100 --> 00:36:11,530
Sir, don't do this.

612
00:36:12,150 --> 00:36:13,390
Let me help you.

613
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,680
You don't need to do this.

614
00:36:20,300 --> 00:36:22,460
Why kill yourself?

615
00:36:25,890 --> 00:36:27,420
You really joined the NBIS.

616
00:36:28,460 --> 00:36:31,450
It's all thanks to Mr. Dai's magnanimity

617
00:36:31,470 --> 00:36:32,730
and open-mindedness,

618
00:36:33,670 --> 00:36:36,750
taking in all the heroes of the world.

619
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:39,690
Why didn't he choose you?

620
00:36:39,860 --> 00:36:41,320
It's true to say

621
00:36:42,240 --> 00:36:45,040
that you're a lackey who has served three masters.

622
00:36:45,370 --> 00:36:47,620
This is the "go with the flow"

623
00:36:47,750 --> 00:36:50,010
that I've been telling you about before.

624
00:36:59,790 --> 00:37:01,120
What are you doing here?

625
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:02,890
I see.

626
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:07,830
You want to sacrifice your life for your Emperor

627
00:37:08,430 --> 00:37:11,320
and gain posthumous fame as a martyred samurai.

628
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:15,220
And you want Gu Yizhong to be your kaishakunin.

629
00:37:16,820 --> 00:37:18,230
Why didn't you help him?

630
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:20,940
Pick up the knife.

631
00:37:21,110 --> 00:37:22,450
With a swift swing,

632
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:23,670
chop off his head

633
00:37:23,780 --> 00:37:26,380
to avenge your father and sister.

634
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:28,690
Come on.

635
00:37:29,430 --> 00:37:30,030
Go on.

636
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:31,930
Finish him.

637
00:37:32,670 --> 00:37:33,190
Take it.

638
00:37:35,830 --> 00:37:36,980
Hurry up.

639
00:37:39,550 --> 00:37:40,550
Gu Yizhong,

640
00:37:41,870 --> 00:37:44,110
you are a scholar after all.

641
00:37:44,740 --> 00:37:45,270
Come on.

642
00:37:46,190 --> 00:37:47,310
Major,

643
00:37:47,630 --> 00:37:49,190
since we've been a part of each other's lives for a while,

644
00:37:49,190 --> 00:37:50,390
let me help you.

645
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:01,120
I was just joking.

646
00:38:03,190 --> 00:38:05,320
I won't let him die like that so easily.

647
00:38:05,710 --> 00:38:06,420
Guards!

648
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:09,090
Take the Jap away

649
00:38:09,210 --> 00:38:10,300
and send him to the prisoner-of-war camp

650
00:38:10,300 --> 00:38:12,430
to await the Military Commission's verdict!

651
00:38:12,430 --> 00:38:13,070
Yes!

652
00:38:20,510 --> 00:38:22,400
Zhou Zhifei!

653
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:25,720
You bastard!

654
00:38:27,630 --> 00:38:28,630
I won't stoop down

655
00:38:29,530 --> 00:38:30,770
to kill him.

656
00:38:33,470 --> 00:38:34,650
Yizhong,

657
00:38:35,910 --> 00:38:36,880
we meet again.

658
00:38:44,190 --> 00:38:47,510
I, as the commander of the Suzhou Special Operations Group

659
00:38:47,910 --> 00:38:49,290
appointed by Mr. Dai

660
00:38:49,940 --> 00:38:52,530
from the Military Commission,

661
00:38:52,670 --> 00:38:54,160
am here to reclaim Suzhou.

662
00:38:54,190 --> 00:38:56,650
I didn't expect my first case to be about you.

663
00:38:57,270 --> 00:38:59,150
You're a traitor.

664
00:39:00,270 --> 00:39:01,330
Surprised, right?

665
00:39:03,660 --> 00:39:05,150
You traitor!

666
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:06,720
If you had any dignity,

667
00:39:07,780 --> 00:39:10,180
you wouldn't dare stand here and talk to me.

668
00:39:11,270 --> 00:39:12,510
How about this?

669
00:39:13,990 --> 00:39:15,950
Let's see if the people of Suzhou

670
00:39:16,330 --> 00:39:17,940
will eat you raw

671
00:39:18,030 --> 00:39:19,830
if we throw you out on the street?

672
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:23,340
The one that the people of Suzhou want to eat raw is you.

673
00:39:23,340 --> 00:39:24,190
No. No.

674
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:25,500
You must think

675
00:39:26,150 --> 00:39:27,840
I'm a traitor as well, right?

676
00:39:29,310 --> 00:39:30,310
"Infiltration,"

677
00:39:30,430 --> 00:39:31,310
remember?

678
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:34,830
I was a traitor sent by the NBIS

679
00:39:34,850 --> 00:39:37,370
to infiltrate No. 90.

680
00:39:37,750 --> 00:39:38,630
And you?

681
00:39:40,470 --> 00:39:41,730
Are you going to tell me

682
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:43,250
it was the New Fourth Army

683
00:39:43,250 --> 00:39:44,510
or the Communist Party

684
00:39:45,030 --> 00:39:46,270
that asked you to infiltrate No. 90?

685
00:39:46,270 --> 00:39:47,910
Didn't you say you weren't?

686
00:39:51,900 --> 00:39:53,990
I don't have time to listen to your nonsense.

687
00:39:53,990 --> 00:39:54,990
I'm going home.

688
00:39:56,390 --> 00:39:56,990
Stop!

689
00:39:58,480 --> 00:39:59,160
Gu Yizhong.

690
00:40:00,630 --> 00:40:01,670
Do you think you can get away

691
00:40:01,670 --> 00:40:03,470
this easily every time?

692
00:40:03,910 --> 00:40:05,380
♫Who am I, who do I stand for?♫

693
00:40:04,440 --> 00:40:06,350
You must face the judgment of history

694
00:40:05,690 --> 00:40:07,380
♫Back to back♫

695
00:40:06,390 --> 00:40:07,510
and the people!

696
00:40:07,600 --> 00:40:09,290
♫When ideals and reality♫

697
00:40:07,830 --> 00:40:09,970
Guards, arrest Gu Yizhong!

698
00:40:09,380 --> 00:40:11,000
♫Are at odds♫

699
00:40:11,500 --> 00:40:13,630
♫Covered in wounds♫

700
00:40:14,300 --> 00:40:17,150
♫Exhausted♫

701
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:20,180
♫Is it a lost path, is it despair♫

702
00:40:20,240 --> 00:40:21,920
♫Or the darkness of night?♫

703
00:40:22,170 --> 00:40:23,940
♫Searching in the lighthouse♫

704
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:25,630
♫For a ray of light♫

705
00:40:26,440 --> 00:40:28,210
♫A wandering heart♫

706
00:40:28,700 --> 00:40:32,370
♫Longs for comfort♫

707
00:40:32,790 --> 00:40:36,010
♫Unable to shed tears♫

708
00:40:36,310 --> 00:40:38,110
Traitor! Traitor!

709
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:39,960
♫What kind of taste is this?♫

710
00:40:40,170 --> 00:40:42,990
♫Used to facing it alone♫

711
00:40:43,100 --> 00:40:47,360
♫Not expecting company♫

712
00:40:47,470 --> 00:40:50,420
♫The closer they are♫

713
00:40:50,860 --> 00:40:54,440
♫The more they are your weakness♫

714
00:40:51,510 --> 00:40:54,390
You bastard!

715
00:40:55,470 --> 00:41:01,960
♫No one is invincible♫

716
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:05,340
♫Lonely souls♫

717
00:41:06,090 --> 00:41:08,560
♫Alone in sorrow♫

718
00:41:09,710 --> 00:41:12,570
♫In silence♫

719
00:41:12,930 --> 00:41:16,850
♫They fear nothing♫

720
00:41:17,670 --> 00:41:20,640
♫Walking alone and returning alone♫

721
00:41:18,140 --> 00:41:21,910
[Celebrate the Victory of the War of Resistance]

722
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:24,760
♫Drunk alone, with only their shadow as company♫

723
00:41:25,190 --> 00:41:27,320
♫A lonely boat♫

724
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:31,870
♫Snuggling up to solitude♫

725
00:41:32,420 --> 00:41:33,680
The Commander is here!

726
00:41:59,880 --> 00:42:01,540
Who's been occupying my house

727
00:42:02,150 --> 00:42:03,740
for the past two years while I've been away?

728
00:42:03,740 --> 00:42:04,610
Sir,

729
00:42:04,710 --> 00:42:08,570
it's Yu Bailu from the Civil Affairs Bureau of Jiangsu Provincial under the Wang Regime.

730
00:42:08,570 --> 00:42:10,020
Where is Yu now?

731
00:42:11,990 --> 00:42:12,750
He ran away.

732
00:42:22,750 --> 00:42:23,990
Tell my wife

733
00:42:24,500 --> 00:42:25,830
that the house is dirty.

734
00:42:25,830 --> 00:42:26,660
I don't want it anymore,

735
00:42:26,660 --> 00:42:28,060
and I'll find a new place.

736
00:42:28,060 --> 00:42:28,550
Yes!

737
00:42:48,850 --> 00:42:51,250
[Loyalty]

738
00:42:52,230 --> 00:42:53,470
Isn't that Gu Yizhong?

739
00:42:53,470 --> 00:42:54,670
Yes. Why is he here?

740
00:42:54,940 --> 00:42:55,670
I don't know.

741
00:42:55,670 --> 00:42:56,750
A big traitor.

742
00:42:56,750 --> 00:42:58,280
He committed so many atrocities.
